    <item>
      <title>We’re at the Beginning of an Infinity of Knowledge</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/were-at-the-beginning-of-an-infinity-of-knowledge/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Mar 2021 15:27:06 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/were-at-the-beginning-of-an-infinity-of-knowledge/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/were-at-the-beginning-of-an-infinity-of-knowledge.zh/&#34;&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://nav.al/knowledge&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://nav.al/knowledge&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://nav.al/knowledge&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;were-at-the-beginning-of-an-infinity-of-knowledge&#34;&gt;We’re at the Beginning of an Infinity of Knowledge&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mar 15 2021&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;&#xA;The difference with &lt;em&gt;The Beginning of Infinity&lt;/em&gt; is you&amp;rsquo;re getting a worldview. You&amp;rsquo;re not getting the standard take from physicists about how to understand quantum theory. You&amp;rsquo;re not getting the standard take of how to understand knowledge from philosophers. And you&amp;rsquo;re certainly not getting the standard take of how to understand mathematics from mathematicians.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Read the Best 100 Books Over and Over Again</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/read-the-best-100-books-over-and-over-again/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Mar 2021 19:05:24 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/read-the-best-100-books-over-and-over-again/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/read-the-best-100-books-over-and-over-again.zh/&#34;&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://nav.al/read&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://nav.al/read&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://nav.al/read&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;read-the-best-100-books-over-and-over-again&#34;&gt;Read the Best 100 Books Over and Over Again&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Mar 10 2021&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Many claim to read, but very few understand&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;em&gt;The Beginning of Infinity&lt;/em&gt; reminds me the most of &lt;em&gt;Gödel, Escher, Bach&lt;/em&gt; in that it is very wide-ranging and stitches together ideas from many different disciplines. It&amp;rsquo;s very difficult to understand and follow completely. Everyone claims to have read it, but, as far as I can tell, very few people understand it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
